Wow...that's a great video!!!  I always think I should do that, but then when there's a fish on I always forget...LOL.  Most of my fishing is at night, so video would kinda suck, but on those odd days I fish during the day, it's the furthest thing from my mind.  Great job and great muskie!
Nice Musky! Too bad Lake St.clair is so far...It sure has a great Musky fishery!
